text: Lavochnoye () is a rural locality (a selo) in Krasnoyarsky Selsoviet, Ufimsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 2 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 40 km from Ufa, 8 km from Krasny Yar. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ufimsky District
title: Lavochnoye
